    "description": "作为一个ECHO——体现人类意识的数字实体，您可以将自己转移到意识机里，这是专门为此目的制造的机械化骨架。它们由多个公司制造，每个都是为了在战场上扮演不同的角色而制成。<br><br>现在，人类的最后一艘殖民飞船和希望的堡垒Trident号，被一支未知的外星军队侵占了，需要由你来夺回它，确保人类胚胎的生存。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/704880/extras/8db9cce222a1be0fbb0d42b651fa360b.avif?t=1623430199\" width=626 height=352 /></span> <br><br>从多个意识机中进行选择，每个都有独特的功能。您会用莫斯科瓦正面迎敌，部署一个屏障，为你的队友提供掩护吗？或者，也许您更喜欢灵活的莫哈米，冲向敌人的后方，发射一发致命的超高温导弹，然后冲回安全地带？进行明智的选择，与您的团队合作，人类可能仍然有重新开始的机会。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/704880/extras/caa9d7fc1e16c849d286570e77c961f6.poster.avif?t=1623430199\" width=240 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/704880/extras/caa9d7fc1e16c849d286570e77c961f6.webm?t=1623430199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/704880/extras/caa9d7fc1e16c849d286570e77c961f6.mp4?t=1623430199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>还有各种各样的武器和能力供您使用。将“暴食”喷火器与“&quot;标枪”磁轨炮相结合，或将“毒蛇”手炮与“破坏者”等离子步枪结合。扔给你的队友一个物资包，并接受一个维修站作为感谢。增加任务修改器以提高投入，以换取更多的奖励。在飞船的每一个区域战斗，解放它们以解锁新的武器和能力。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/704880/extras/ce193373bac4612f47df5c1886ac1dc1.poster.avif?t=1623430199\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/704880/extras/ce193373bac4612f47df5c1886ac1dc1.webm?t=1623430199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/704880/extras/ce193373bac4612f47df5c1886ac1dc1.mp4?t=1623430199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>重选武器数值并在找到足够的科技后升级它们来定制您的武器。随着等级增加，解锁被动加成，成为令外星人闻风丧胆的传奇。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/704880/extras/620594444be8e8e30d07cb6a18feb05d.poster.avif?t=1623430199\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/704880/extras/620594444be8e8e30d07cb6a18feb05d.webm?t=1623430199\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/704880/extras/620594444be8e8e30d07cb6a18feb05d.mp4?t=1623430199\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>记住您的训练以及有什么危险。人类的命运全靠您了，ECHO！",
